
<%- include('header.ejs'); -%>
<body style="margin-bottom: 5rem">
  <%- include('nav.ejs'); -%>

<!-- User and General posted questions -->
<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row">
      <!-- User posted questions -->
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h3 class="mb-0">User posted questions</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="list-group">
              <% data.forEach((x)=> { %>
                <div class="list-group-item">
                  <h5 class="mb-1">Question:</h5>
                  <p class="mb-1"><%= x.quest %></p>
                  <h6 class="mb-1">Answer:</h6>
                  <p class="mb-1"><%= x.ans %></p>
                </div>
              <% }) %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <!-- General posted questions -->
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h3 class="mb-0">General posted questions</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="list-group">
              <!-- Add your data for general questions here -->
              <div class="list-group-item">
                <p><strong>Question1:How can I access the health insurance guidance on your web application?</p></strong>
                <p>Navigate to the "Services" section and click on "Health Insurance." Our user-friendly platform will guide you through the process.</p>
                <p><strong>Question2:What types of part-time job opportunities are available for international students?</p></strong>
                <p>Explore our "Part-Time Jobs" section to discover a range of employment opportunities tailored to international students.</p>
                <p><strong>Question2:What types of part-time job opportunities are available for international students?</p></strong>
                <p>Explore our "Part-Time Jobs" section to discover a range of employment opportunities tailored to international students.</p>
                <p><strong>Question3:How does your accommodations assistance work?</p></strong>
                <p>Find suitable and affordable housing options by visiting the "Accommodations Assistance" section. We provide resources and support to meet your preferences and budget.
                </p>
                <p><strong>Question4:How do I customize my resume for part-time job applications?</p></strong>
                <p>Follow the steps outlined in the "Part-Time Jobs" page to build an effective resume tailored to the specific job you're applying for.</p>
                <p><strong>Question5:Can you provide tips for building a strong part-time job resume?</p></strong>
                <p>Refer to the "Tips for Building a Strong Part-Time Job Resume" section for valuable advice on customizing your resume, quantifying achievements, and more.</p>
                <p><strong>Question6:What kind of interview questions should I prepare for part-time job interviews?</p></strong>
                <p>Watch our recommended video lectures on job interview questions in the "Video Lectures References" section for insights into common interview questions and effective responses.</p>
                <p><strong>Question7:How can I handle challenging situations at work as an international student?
                </p></strong>
                <p>Read through the sample interview questions and answers provided in the "Sample Interview Questions" section for guidance on handling challenging work scenarios.</p>
                <p><strong>Question8:What languages should I highlight on my resume as an international student?</p></strong>
                <p>In the "Tips for Building a Strong Part-Time Job Resume" section, we recommend highlighting additional languages and specifying your proficiency level.</p>
                <p><strong>Question9:Where can I find information about the best part-time jobs for teenagers?</p></strong>
                <p>Check out the external link provided in the "Video Lectures References" section for insights into the best part-time jobs for teenagers.</p>
                <p><strong>Question10:How do I contact International Students Assistance for further assistance?</p></strong>
                <p>Visit our "Contact Us" page for information on reaching out to us through email, phone, office visits, or social media. We are here to assist you with any inquiries.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <!-- Post a Question -->
    <div class="row mt-5">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h3 class="mb-0">Post a Question</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <form action="/faq" method="post">
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="question">Your Question:</label>
                <textarea class="form-control" id="question" name="question" rows="4"></textarea>
              </div>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Submit Question</button>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
  
        <!-- Error message -->
        <div class="mt-3">
          <p id="errors" class="text-success">
            <div class="alert alert-success">
              <% if(typeof(error) != 'undefined') { %>
                <%= error %>
              <% } %>
            </div>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  

</body>
<%- include('footer.ejs'); -%>
